{meta: artist Ralph Stanley}

{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[C]Sadly we sing and with tremulous [F]breath
[C]As we stand by the mystical [G7]stream
[C]In the valley and by the dark river of [F]death
[C]And yet ’tis no [G7]more than a [C]dream
{end_of_verse}

